Instruction: With all switches ON and the battery inserted, measure the voltage between the two wires on the output side of control module 3 and the two wires on the input side of control module 4. Verify that module 3 output has 12 V relative to its return, and whether that same pair is correctly connected (no polarity inversion, no open) to module 4 input.
